body_html:
To install tensorflow on windows, whl file is created at
tensorflow\contrib\cmake\build\tf_python\dist.
I followed below instruction.
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/cmake/README.md
To build and out whl, below command is necessary.
MSBuild /p:Configuration=Release tf_python_build_pip_package.vcxproj
Still, same error with recent git.

2016-11-16 13:40 GMT+09:00 Derek Murray notifications@github.com:

It sounds like you have an old copy of tensorflow/python/ops/gen_
array_ops.py that wasn't generated after updating past a41f0ea
a41f0ea
(which updates hidden_ops.txt). Could you try deleting the tf_python/
directory and rerunning the build?

—
